com.nokia.maps.search

Interface SearchRequest

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    GeocodeRequest, PlaceSearchRequest, ReverseGeocodeRequest
    Deprecated. 
    use Request

    public interface SearchRequest
    This interface represents a search request. The SearchRequest is an interface common to all three search types, namely GeocodeRequest, ReverseGeocodeRequest and PlaceSearchRequest
